title: Presidents Day 2010 720p BluRay
description:
===================================================================================
It's campaign season| and the students of Lincoln High are buzzing about who's going to be class president... But when a psycho dressed as Abraham Lincoln starts
hacking up students| the candidates must run... for their lives. One-by-one| the mighty Lincoln Lambs are being slaughtered by the merciless maniac in the stovepipe
hat. Everyone is dying for a vote...
